    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make parking on footpaths illegal in England",
        "additional_details": "We believe footpaths are exactly as described for the public to freely walk without hindrance from parked vehicles. Keep car parking away from footpaths, with enforcement powers given to local councils to punish those who do block footpaths.",
        "background": "Make parking on footpaths illegal for the whole of England.",
